\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 The book of Malachi\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I believe every great story has to start with a problem.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And too often we jump right into the good part of the story\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is what happens with Christmas. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We jump right into the part where Jesus comes (sorry spoiler alert if you didn\'92t know that)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But that isn\'92t where the story starts\'85in fact we don\'92t have enough time to go back to the beginning\'85but I want to read you something from the book of Malachi\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
