\f4\i great and dreadful
\f3\i0  day of the\'a0Lord\'a0comes.\
\
\'a0
\f2\b \super 6\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub He will turn the hearts of the parents to their children,\'a0and the hearts of the children to their parents; or 
\f4\i else
\f3\i0  I will come and strike\'a0the land with 
\f4\i total destruction
\f3\i0 .\'94  Malachi 4\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now you may be new to spiritual things but when the God you worship tells you that He\'92s mad at you\'85you are doing things wrong and stealing from Him.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Then the last words he says are that there is a possibility that He will strike the last with TOTAL DESTRUCTION!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}To make it worse\'85this was the last thing God said to them\'85for 400 years\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Not 4, not 40, 400 years.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There was 400 years of silence and sin\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The nation of Israel was overrun by other powers and authorities.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They were slaves to other nations and the gods of those nations \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf3 Transition:  But we miss that because we just turn a page and we\'92re onto the next part.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}400 years are in between this page and the previous one\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}10 generations come and go\'85and nothing.  God is silent\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They are lost and more importantly the last thing He said to them was not encouraging.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It was not a going away love letter but a sharp rebuke with an ultimatum that appears in their eyes to becoming true.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some of you feel that way right now?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your story is their story\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You feel as those God is angry with you and abandoned you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For some you went to a church or to a friend for advice and all you heard was God\'92s anger yelled at you.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The preacher was mad or angry or Baptist.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And you walked away and haven\'92t heard from God since\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s been years\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1
\f1\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s not that you don\'92t believe in God\'85it\'92s just that you think He is mad at you and you\'92re not on speaking terms.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Transition:  There was 400 of silence and it\'92s not that nothing happened during that period\'85it\'92s just that God doesn\'92t seem interested in telling that story anymore\'85He\'92s moved on\'85.\
\
\
\
\
