\f1\b \cf3 Transition:  Here is why so many don\'92t experience Christmas\'85\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f0\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He is interested in telling a different story\'85a God sized story\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I have sat with this for years trying to figure this out.  Why does God do this?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
