\
\
(need to connect God turning the page with God wanting us to turn the page)\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And while you keep wanting to talk about what happened in your past and what went wrong and how you can\'92t do it\'85God is telling you\'85TURN THE PAGE\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Quit focusing on the past, quit focusing on the irrelevant, quit focusing on the foolish\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Turn the Page\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f0\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You keep wanting to reread the old you.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You keep wanting to reread the old story \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is calling you to turn the page tonight\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}To start a new chapter in your life\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}To begin a new journey with Him\'85all you have to do is turn the page\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Quit looking back and start looking to the future\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Quit looking at what you\'92ve done and look at what God\'92s done\uc0\u8232 (rant here)\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
Listen to me\'85you will never move forward until\'85you turn the page and start to read a different story!\
\
\
\
And that story is Jesus!  \
That you can\'92t but He can\
That there isn\'92t enough help in the world to get you there but there is finally hope\
\
\
\
Did you know that you\'92re not in the Christmas story?  You know why? \
\
\
\
HOW DO I TURN THE PAGE?\
