\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 As a church we believe Hope changes everything.\
That is why this Christmas we set out to inspire as many people as possible with random acts of generousity.\
As we looked at the Gospels we saw that Jesus not only taught people he helped them.\
He helped them with practical things like food and being healed\
And it was the simple things He did for others that inspired so many around Him\
It\'92s what made Him different from every other religious leader.\
So this Christmas we started asking the question \
What if the church starting acting like Jesus?\
What if that overflow of our Hope we have impacted our daily decisions?\
What if we were serious about loving our neighbor as our self?\
\
\
